subject: Olympic Games (2012)
Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Meseret Defar won the 5,000 meters, defeating Tirunesh Dibaba, a fellow Ethiopian who was fatigued from her gold-medal effort in the 10,000 as well as an undisclosed pre-Olympics illness.
